title: Great Neighborhood Outdoor Kitchen 872 Jodee Ln.
text:
Great Neighborhood Outdoor Kitchen 872 Jodee Ln. ad date: 10/17/2015 
872 Jodee Ln. Brookings The neighborhood is outstanding and so is this single level home with 3 bdrms, 2 baths, and bonus room that can be used as office space or an additional dining room. Granite kitchen with a bamboo wall and accents. Large windows look out to a private back yard oasis with covered patio, a shop, a finished shed that is used as an art studio. Outdoor kitchen for grilling, a sink, cook-top and a pizza oven for outdoor entertaining. A must see! No. 15459212 $347,000 Jude Hodge, Broker
